{"tid":620352,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"因為一句「還掂都係」，尋晚被人嬲到而家","createTime":"2018-04-07T13:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T02:53:08.000Z","uid":78971,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e6988344e645a0c38407821ea24203c6deddda4","tid":620352,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:28:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n尋晚同班兄弟食飯，阿強就帶咗個女朋友出嚟，我哋都係第一次見佢呢個女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n咁我另外一個兄弟阿樂就講啲客套說話，讚下阿強女朋友啦<br />\n<br />\n阿樂就話：「阿嫂又高又靚女，又有身材，阿強就執到啦！😂🤣」<br />\n<br />\n咁阿強女朋友就紅都面晒咁啦<br />\n<br />\n阿強就爆咗句「還掂都係！梗係揀個靚架啦！」<br />\n<br />\n咁大家都笑嘅<br />\n唯獨是佢女朋友笑唔出<br />\n<br />\n散場之後，阿強突然send個msg去Group話：<br />\n<br />\n「佢係咁問我句「還掂都係」係咩意思呀🌚🤦🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n問我係咪「還掂都係玩下就算」，定「還掂都係中出即飛」，定「還掂都係雞」，而家唔知點好呀，救命呀咁多位大佬」<br />\n<br />\n我：還掂都係，分手啦<br />\n<br />\n阿強就冇再上過水<br />\n而家好擔心佢<br />\n<br />\n阿強見字請回。<br />\n<br />\n暴走梳乎厘 字"},{"pid":"f3222e4ed2ab40fbcf806d3c26bc2a4102956673","tid":620352,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:32:33.000Z","msg":"阿強！"},{"pid":"f284910b839fbc12ff50d04dd2924d1a90a264e8","tid":620352,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:35:12.000Z","msg":"私家雞同公家雞既分別姐"},{"pid":"258deb9e2902e8e7adcd3ba6a64aa01a8011cacd","tid":620352,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f284910b839fbc12ff50d04dd2924d1a90a264e8","tid":620352,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:35:12.000Z","msg":"私家雞同公家雞既分別姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfd907dc2de51fda3e8c85ac4b635e1a627004a","tid":620352,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:53:12.000Z","msg":"阿強，打牌喇"},{"pid":"1faefca0e6f1f1271c127cde66f1ec13aed2cd95","tid":620352,"uid":48611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"7/10 不能再多"},{"pid":"1f05502e85a4